snippet.title: freepocket4me
snippet.description:
My Nirvana

my  white corner
"Yo soy pertenece  a una raza antigua de pies descalzos
y de sueños blancos"
         ***
"An invisible red thread connects those destined to meet,regardless of  time,place or circumstances.The thread may stretch  or tangle,but never break."
(ancient chinese proverb)
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FehY8mjd9Bk
 
"Whoever fights monsters should see to it that in the process he does not become a monster. And if you gaze long enough into an abyss, the abyss will gaze back into you."
Friedrich Nietzsche

Thanks for  all comments,no matter how is sound, or look like:) Unfortunately I`m not able to reply them how is not in my intention to connect myself via google plus, Otherwise,I`d would be more than happy to answer at each one,here.Also I must thank for all of you, whom  find worthly to subscribe at my channel, I`m grateful and  I appreciate your action to do that!:)
